<li id="cite_note-47"><b><a href="#cite_ref-47" title="">^</a></b> This was not an official town meeting, but a gathering of "the body of the people" of <a href="/wiki/Greater_Boston" title="Greater Boston">greater Boston</a>; Alexander, <i>Revolutionary Politician</i>, 123.</li>
