<li><a href="/wiki/Pauline_Maier" title="Pauline Maier">Maier, Pauline</a>. <i>The Old Revolutionaries: Political Lives in the Age of Samuel Adams</i>. New York: Knopf, 1980. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0394510968" class="internal">ISBN 0-394-51096-8</a>.</li>
