<li>Thomas, Peter D. G. <i>Tea Party to Independence: The Third Phase of the American Revolution, 1773–1776</i>. Oxford: Clarendon Press, 1991. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0198201427" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-820142-7</a>.</li>
<li>Young, Alfred F. <i>The Shoemaker and the Tea Party: Memory and the American Revolution.</i> Boston: Beacon Press, 1999. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0807054054" class="internal">ISBN 0807054054</a>; <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780807054055" class="internal">ISBN 978-0807054055</a>.</li>
